Hello @soundsright・105 

Subnet version `2.0.0` has been merged to `main`. The subnet is now hosting 48kHz competitions! 🔥 

**This is a mandatory update for both miners and validators.** Also, just a reminder for validators--please update your .env files to include your ElevenLabs API key, as OpenAI is no longer needed!

🛠️ Release notes:

- Added 48kHz competitions
- Revamped score distribution per task/sample rate/metric
- Dataset generation now uses ElevenLabs TTS
- /reset/ endpoint added to model API
- Validator cache reset
- Adjust competition length to 3 days
- Adjust model timeouts based on sample rate

Please let us know if you have any questions or concerns. Cheers!
Seems your validator has prev cache as well even tho updated codebase.
